      <description>Hello Matthieu,&#13;
&#13;
for this use case we developed an extension.&#13;
&#13;
You can define an aspect ratio for the image e.g. 3:4 and than you have a rectangle to choose the image extract.&#13;
Then you have the original and the original_crop as an reference image. On top of these you can create cropped or non cropped image variations.&#13;
&#13;
Is this what you want?</description>
